ğŸ“ Project Structure
File	Description
login.php	User/Admin login
register.php	User registration
logout.php	Logout functionality
admin_dashboard.php	Admin home/dashboard
user_dashboard.php	User home/dashboard
add_product.php	Admin adds new product
edit_product.php	Admin edits a product
delete_product.php	Admin deletes a product
generate_coupon.php	Users generate coupons
redeem_coupon.php	Users redeem coupons
view_coupon.php	Admin views all coupons
my_coupon.php	Users view their own coupons
db.php	Database connection
ğŸš€ How to Use
ğŸ”‘ Admin

Login using the default admin credentials.

Add Products via add_product.php:

Name

Price (in USD)

Discount (1% to 100%)

View a list of products in a table on the dashboard.

Edit or delete products using respective buttons.

View all coupons generated by users along with their status and associated user info.

ğŸ‘¥ User

Register via register.php with your email and password.

Login to access the user dashboard.

View products available for discount coupons.

Generate coupons using the "Generate Coupon" button.

Each product allows only one coupon per user.

Once a coupon is generated, the button will be disabled.

View your coupons in my_coupon.php.

Redeem your coupons any time. Upon successful redemption, youâ€™ll receive a confirmation alert.

